# Allowlist approach: track only text audit artifacts, ignore everything else.
# The binary curriculum source (decks, worksheets, tests, images, archives)
# lives canonically in Google Drive — these are working copies, kept out of
# git to avoid bloat and useless binary diffs. Ignoring everything by default
# means no new binary format can leak in; we opt in text types explicitly.

# Ignore everything...
*

# ...but keep directory traversal, and opt in the text we want.
!*/
!.gitignore
!*.md
!*.csv
!*.txt

# Note: progress.log (.log) stays ignored on purpose — it's rewritten fresh
# each session per CLAUDE.md convention, so it would only add churn.
